<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title"><strong>The Fed Looks Set to Make a Dangerous Mistake</strong> <span class="divider"> | </span></span> Raising rates in the near future would be a serious error that would threaten all of the Fedâs major objectives, Lawrence Summers argues. <br /><span class="kicker"><a href="//www.ft.com/intl/cms/s/2/f664a7e0-4978-11e5-b558-8a9722977189.html#axzz3jhfHqlSc"> THE FINANCIAL TIMES </a></span></p>
